1
00:00:02,370 --> 00:00:03,920
Foto ini kocak, 'kan?!

2
00:00:05,340 --> 00:00:06,990
Kocak! Kocak!

3
00:00:07,050 --> 00:00:08,570
Asli kocak!

4
00:00:08,760 --> 00:00:09,820
Kocak banget!

5
00:00:09,840 --> 00:00:11,140
Iya, 'kan?

6
00:00:11,290 --> 00:00:12,960
Berisik banget!

7
00:00:15,770 --> 00:00:16,740
Woi!

8
00:00:16,830 --> 00:00:17,720
Hah?

9
00:00:19,460 --> 00:00:21,020
Hi-Hina?!

10
00:00:21,270 --> 00:00:23,100
Kalian menghabiskan tempat!

11
00:00:23,150 --> 00:00:25,400
Kalau lagi lengang,
enggak masalah.

12
00:00:25,520 --> 00:00:27,590
Tapi ada nenek-nenek lagi berdiri, 'kan?

13
00:00:27,750 --> 00:00:29,330
Bagilah tempat untuk beliau.

14
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:31,650
Oke.

15
00:00:31,650 --> 00:00:33,280
Lebih mepet lagi.

16
00:00:34,390 --> 00:00:35,520
'Makasih, ya!

17
00:00:35,550 --> 00:00:37,590
- Wih.
- Imutnya.

18
00:00:37,710 --> 00:00:40,060
Nek, silakan duduk.

19
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:43,390
Wah, mohon maaf merepotkanmu, ya.

20
00:00:43,550 --> 00:00:46,240
Hina memang hebat!

21
00:00:48,220 --> 00:00:52,870
Kerah kami ditarik, dan diberi bogem mentah

22
00:00:53,130 --> 00:00:57,730
sehingga kami sempoyongan,
lalu jongkok bersebelahan

23
00:00:57,770 --> 00:01:02,560
Di tengah hujan yang diprediksi,
kau menyeringai

24
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:08,400
lalu berbohong bahwa "luka pasti akan sembuh"

25
00:01:08,840 --> 00:01:11,420
Bahkan adu mulut yang sering dilakukan

26
00:01:12,090 --> 00:01:16,660
tak bisa kulakukan dengan baik

27
00:01:16,820 --> 00:01:21,720
Jangan katakan candaan
yang membosankan

28
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:26,970
Rasa bosannya pun tampak jelas di mataku!

29
00:01:27,030 --> 00:01:34,670
Tak peduli walau seberapa banyak air
mata yang mengaliri pipi lebamku ini

30
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:41,340
melalui hati yang goyah
bersanding dengan bahu

31
00:01:41,410 --> 00:01:45,900
kau pasti bisa menghindari
akhir buruk yang menghantui!

32
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:51,470
Kenapa rasa sakit ini lebih
nyaman dibanding kebahagiaan?

33
00:01:51,580 --> 00:01:55,840
Bahkan rasa sakit ini kian menggema!

34
00:01:55,920 --> 00:02:00,480
Sambil menggigit lidah dan
mengenakan baju basah,

35
00:02:00,520 --> 00:02:03,690
mari kita tertawakan wajah sembap ini

36
00:02:04,060 --> 00:02:08,430
Lalu di tengah malam bermandikan hujan

37
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:16,200
kita ikrarkan balas dendam!

38
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:24,240
(#4 Kembali)

39
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:21,230
'Makasih karena mau
menemaniku belanja.

40
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:23,100
Ya, enggak masalah, kok.

41
00:02:23,230 --> 00:02:24,910
'Gimana UAS-mu?

42
00:02:25,050 --> 00:02:28,180
Wah, UAS rasanya nostalgia banget!

43
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:30,860
Nostalgia?
Belum lama ini, loh.

44
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,900
Ah, enggak.
Benar juga!

45
00:02:33,079 --> 00:02:35,570
Gawat, aku keceplosan!

46
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:39,810
Mari belajar yang giat.
Kamu punya impian, 'kan?

47
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,360
Impian?

48
00:02:41,730 --> 00:02:43,880
Loh, aku punya impian, ya?

49
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:48,300
Oke, telah kuputuskan!

50
00:02:48,490 --> 00:02:49,329
Hah?

51
00:02:50,170 --> 00:02:52,470
Hina akan mengajarimu!

52
00:02:58,090 --> 00:02:59,170
Kamu kenapa?

53
00:02:59,850 --> 00:03:03,290
Yah, rasanya baru kali ini,
aku masuk kamar cewek!

54
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:05,840
Jangan jelalatan!

55
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:07,160
Maaf, deh.

56
00:03:07,370 --> 00:03:09,060
Dasar enggak sopan.

57
00:03:09,090 --> 00:03:10,390
Maaf, ya.

58
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:13,650
Karena mendadak, jadinya Ibu
enggak mempersiapkan apa-apa.

59
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:17,210
Padahal baru kali ini Hina
mengajak cowok kemari!

60
00:03:17,310 --> 00:03:19,790
- Mama!
- Walah, tidak usah repot-repot.

61
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:23,520
Wah, rupanya imut juga.
Sejak kapan kalian akrab? Sekelas?

62
00:03:23,550 --> 00:03:25,840
Sudahlah, Mama!
Keluar aja!

63
00:03:25,860 --> 00:03:27,170
Eh?

64
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:27,990
Pacarmu?

65
00:03:28,010 --> 00:03:29,350
Mama!

66
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:32,690
Aku gagal paham.

67
00:03:33,310 --> 00:03:36,329
Oh, iya.
Terima kasih soal adikku, ya.

68
00:03:36,470 --> 00:03:37,230
Hah?

69
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:40,300
Katanya, kamu menolongnya
saat dikepung berandalan.

70
00:03:41,480 --> 00:03:45,490
Papaku jarang
di rumah karena sibuk.

71
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:48,440
Padahal dia benci
papanya yang sesibuk itu,

72
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:51,640
tapi tempo hari dia tiba-tiba bilang
ingin jadi seperti ayah.

73
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:52,840
Hm?

74
00:03:54,550 --> 00:03:56,620
Papaku petugas kepolisian.

75
00:03:56,810 --> 00:03:57,690
Ah!

76
00:03:57,970 --> 00:04:00,440
Itulah kenapa Naoto jadi polisi, ya?!

77
00:04:00,510 --> 00:04:03,680
Eh? Dia belum jadi polisi.
Masih kecil juga.

78
00:04:03,790 --> 00:04:05,400
I-I-Iya juga, ya!

79
00:04:06,020 --> 00:04:07,820
Aku bicara apa, sih?

80
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:12,440
Tapi, mungkin aku yang
ditolong olehnya.

81
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:13,510
Eh?

82
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:16,890
Kurasa dia bakal jadi petugas
kepolisian yang baik!

83
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:20,640
Yah, kayaknya dia juga bakal
jadi orang yang tak segan-segan.

84
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:23,370
Takemichi, kamu sudah berubah, ya.

85
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:25,360
Be-Benarkah?!

86
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,860
Bagian mananya?

87
00:04:28,170 --> 00:04:33,120
Kesannya kamu semakin baik,
atau terkesan kayak orang dewasa.

88
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:36,210
Aku serasa bicara dengan
orang yang jauh lebih tua!

89
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,390
Eh?

90
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,560
Wajar! Soalnya aku 12 tahun lebih tua!

91
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:44,320
Mungkinkah itu termasuk bagian
dirimu yang belum Hina tahu?

92
00:04:44,420 --> 00:04:45,300
Eh?

93
00:04:46,090 --> 00:04:49,610
Hina ingin tahu lebih banyak tentangmu.

94
00:04:55,570 --> 00:04:57,210
Ah, kembang api!

95
00:04:57,330 --> 00:04:59,950
Oh, iya! Hari ini festival kembang api!

96
00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:00,880
Eh?

97
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:07,290
Ayo lihat kembang apinya dari atap!

98
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:09,660
Wah, hebatnya!
Hebat!

99
00:05:11,340 --> 00:05:12,750
Indahnya!

100
00:05:13,280 --> 00:05:16,330
Buruan kemari, Takemichi!

101
00:05:18,860 --> 00:05:21,660
Gawat, aku merasa senang!

102
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:25,700
Aku tak merasakan ini
di kehidupanku sebelumnya.

103
00:05:27,550 --> 00:05:29,310
Loh, bentuk hati?

104
00:05:29,460 --> 00:05:30,970
Hei, kamu lihat yang barusan?

105
00:05:31,220 --> 00:05:32,870
Aku ingin terus berada di sini.

106
00:05:34,050 --> 00:05:36,159
Aku tak ingin kembali
ke masa depan.

107
00:05:36,700 --> 00:05:39,920
Soalnya di masa depan, Hina ...

108
00:05:40,550 --> 00:05:41,740
... tidak ada.

109
00:05:44,590 --> 00:05:46,650
Pegangan tangan boleh kali, ya?

110
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:55,400
Hangatnya.

111
00:06:00,130 --> 00:06:01,440
Hina.

112
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:04,010
Hm?

113
00:06:05,290 --> 00:06:07,150
Ha-Halo.

114
00:06:07,850 --> 00:06:09,090
Naoto?!

115
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:12,360
Jabat tangan denganku
adalah pemicunya.

116
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:16,850
Na-Naoto?!

117
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,890
Loh, kamu juga kemari?

118
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:19,680
Iya.

119
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:24,000
Tidak mungkiiiiiin!

120
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:27,870
Takemichi!

121
00:06:28,490 --> 00:06:30,320
Aku kembali lagi kemari!

122
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,130
Hah?

123
00:06:31,130 --> 00:06:33,890
Berarti, kau pergi ke masa lalu, ya?

124
00:06:34,350 --> 00:06:36,550
Jabat tangan memanglah pemicunya!

125
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:39,960
Kenapa kau ada di sana, sih?!

126
00:06:39,980 --> 00:06:41,830
Eh? Apa maksudmu?

127
00:06:43,409 --> 00:06:46,300
Pokoknya, teoriku tidaklah salah!

128
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,360
Iya, iya.
Benar juga.

129
00:06:48,420 --> 00:06:50,080
Lalu kau sudah kembali lagi.

130
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,470
Eh?

131
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:54,490
Aku sudah mengerti semuanya.

132
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:58,850
Bagaimana keadaan di sana?
Kau kembali karena sudah ada perkembangan, 'kan?

133
00:06:59,390 --> 00:07:01,460
Eng ....

134
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:04,450
Kau berjabat tangan
karena salah orang?!

135
00:07:04,650 --> 00:07:06,340
Yang becus, dong!

136
00:07:07,020 --> 00:07:10,540
Ada hal yang kupahami setelah
kau melintasi waktu kedua kalinya.

137
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:11,750
Oh?

138
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:17,800
Kekuatan melintasi waktumu itu adalah kembali
ke hari yang sama pada 12 tahun lalu.

139
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:19,840
Contohnya,

140
00:07:20,010 --> 00:07:23,610
kalau sekarang kembali ke masa lalu, kau akan
sampai di hari yang sama pada 12 tahun lalu.

141
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:27,120
Jika kau habiskan 1 minggu di sana,
lalu kembali ke sini,

142
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:29,120
waktu di sini pun telah berlalu 1 minggu.

143
00:07:29,130 --> 00:07:30,470
Begitulah intinya.

144
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:33,120
Lalu, selama kau kembali
ke masa lalu,

145
00:07:33,530 --> 00:07:36,330
tubuhmu berada dalam keadaan mati suri.

146
00:07:36,670 --> 00:07:38,800
Eh? Berarti aku kayak orang meninggal?

147
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:42,909
Artinya, tubuhmu di sini
hanyalah wadah hampa.

148
00:07:44,050 --> 00:07:45,640
Makanya, disebut mati suri, ya?

149
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:50,380
Karena berbahaya, sebaiknya kau
melintasi waktu di kamarku saja.

150
00:07:50,840 --> 00:07:55,000
Lalu, misimu mencegah pertemuan
Kisaki dan Sano apakah berhasil?

151
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:56,620
Eng ....

152
00:07:56,850 --> 00:07:58,700
Aku sudah bertemu Bang Mikey, kok.

153
00:07:58,930 --> 00:07:59,720
Mikey?

154
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:01,640
Oh, maksudnya Sano.

155
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:05,510
Dengarlah, Naoto!
Walau Mikey berandalan, tetapi dia orang baik!

156
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,520
Hah?

157
00:08:06,780 --> 00:08:08,540
Kenapa kau tak membunuhnya?!

158
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:10,070
Eh? Membunuh?

159
00:08:10,170 --> 00:08:14,220
Yang membunuh Kakakku itu orang baik?
Kau sudah terbuai masa lalu, ya?!

160
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:14,870
Bukan!

161
00:08:14,940 --> 00:08:15,870
Dengar, ya!

162
00:08:16,050 --> 00:08:21,510
Mikey itu dalang dari banyak kejahatan,
bahkan polisi pun kesulitan menanganinya!

163
00:08:21,710 --> 00:08:25,390
Kalau bisa, aku ingin membunuhnya
dengan tangan ini!

164
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:35,950
Naoto.

165
00:08:36,490 --> 00:08:38,220
Ayo temui Bang Mikey.

166
00:08:38,340 --> 00:08:39,440
Bahaya!

167
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:42,669
Aku ingin menemuinya,
dan bertanya langsung padanya.

168
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:44,930
Sia-sia saja pertanyaanmu!

169
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:48,000
Bang Mikey itu orang
yang dapat dipercaya!

170
00:08:48,330 --> 00:08:52,520
Aku ingin mendengar alasannya
mengenai perubahan Touman!

171
00:08:53,490 --> 00:08:57,420
Sebelum kembali lagi ke masa lalu,
aku ingin memastikannya.

172
00:08:59,570 --> 00:09:01,830
Marilah cari Bang Mikey bersama.

173
00:09:02,310 --> 00:09:03,830
Tolonglah, Naoto.

174
00:09:08,940 --> 00:09:11,530
Meski aku tak tahu apa
yang terjadi di masa lalu,

175
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,530
tetapi kau sudah berubah, Takemichi.

176
00:09:13,770 --> 00:09:15,740
Eh? Benarkah?

177
00:09:15,850 --> 00:09:17,020
Apanya?

178
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:19,450
Sisi lemahmu menghilang.

179
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:21,740
Walau sedikit saja, sih.

180
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:25,020
Eh, apa maksudnya aku semakin keren?

181
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:27,510
Oke, ayo cari cara bertemu Mikey.

182
00:09:27,530 --> 00:09:30,150
Hei, hei.
Ataukah aku tambah rupawan?

183
00:09:30,240 --> 00:09:31,290
Hei, hei!

184
00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:33,040
Langsung kepedean.

185
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:35,040
Takemichi, sortir berkasnya.

186
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:40,680
Geng Tokyo Manji memang gila.

187
00:09:41,140 --> 00:09:43,510
Kewaspadaannya Mikey sangatlah mengerikan.

188
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:45,770
Polisi pun kesulitan melacaknya.

189
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:50,300
Nomor teleponnya mungkin
pakai identitas palsu.

190
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,550
Siapa nih?

191
00:09:52,690 --> 00:09:53,450
Hm?

192
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:57,890
Petinggi Touman.

193
00:09:58,060 --> 00:10:01,310
Sendou Atsushi itu ... Akkun!

194
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,420
Akkun?

195
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:06,250
Temanmu?

196
00:10:06,390 --> 00:10:07,160
Ya!

197
00:10:08,060 --> 00:10:09,640
Aneh.

198
00:10:10,190 --> 00:10:15,140
Dia ditangkap saat umur 16 tahun karena menusuk
anggota Touman bernama Kiyomizu Masataka.

199
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:18,440
Setelah bebas dari penjara,
dia menjadi penjahat kelas teri.

200
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:23,250
Aku tadi ingin menusuk Kiyomasa.

201
00:10:23,710 --> 00:10:25,390
Seingatku, dia berkata begitu!

202
00:10:25,740 --> 00:10:26,880
Jangan-jangan!

203
00:10:26,940 --> 00:10:28,670
Ini terjadi karena masa lalu berubah?!

204
00:10:29,620 --> 00:10:34,020
Akkun tidak jadi ditangkap polisi
karena tidak menusuk Kiyomasa.

205
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:37,740
Karena kau akrab dengan
Bang Mikey, maka Sendou ....

206
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:40,840
Akkun menjadi petinggi Touman?!

207
00:10:43,330 --> 00:10:45,960
Oh, iya. Bisakah kau
menghubungi Sendou?

208
00:10:46,070 --> 00:10:47,880
Eh, bisa.

209
00:10:48,180 --> 00:10:49,800
Kalau nomornya tidak berubah.

210
00:10:50,090 --> 00:10:54,230
Jika menjadi petinggi Touman,
pasti dia terhubung dengan Mikey!

211
00:10:54,310 --> 00:10:55,110
Ah!

212
00:10:58,340 --> 00:11:00,460
Bersiaplah karena kamarku kotor.

213
00:11:00,630 --> 00:11:03,140
Yah, aku sudah bisa membayangkannya.

214
00:11:03,410 --> 00:11:05,500
Buset!
Kotor banget!

215
00:11:05,850 --> 00:11:07,670
Makanya kuminta kau bersiap.

216
00:11:07,820 --> 00:11:09,760
Apa ini bisa ditinggali manusia?!

217
00:11:09,890 --> 00:11:12,110
Tunggu sebentar, ya.

218
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:16,060
Aku lagi mencari catatan
yang dulu kupakai.

219
00:11:16,530 --> 00:11:17,400
Tunggu ....

220
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:20,860
Duh, debunya bisa bikin gatal-gatal!

221
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:22,320
Aku beli masker dulu!

222
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:24,750
Sambil lari, gih!

223
00:11:28,110 --> 00:11:28,920
Eh?

224
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:32,950
Ah, ketemu!
Ini dia!

225
00:11:33,130 --> 00:11:35,270
Wah, nostalgianya!

226
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:38,240
Kenangan masa lalu
seakan bangkit!

227
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:41,420
Apa-apaan orang ini?
Nostalgia!

228
00:11:41,710 --> 00:11:44,200
Bisakah segera diselesaikan?

229
00:11:44,410 --> 00:11:45,800
Ah, oke.

230
00:11:45,940 --> 00:11:48,240
Akkun, ya. Tahu, kok.

231
00:11:49,520 --> 00:11:50,750
Ada!

232
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:53,590
Semoga saja belum berubah.

233
00:12:00,250 --> 00:12:01,400
Akkun.

234
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:04,440
Sampai besok.

235
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:06,380
Dadah.

236
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:11,630
Seluruh tubuhku sakit!

237
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:14,000
Hei, Akkun.

238
00:12:14,290 --> 00:12:14,890
Hm?

239
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:19,850
Seandainya, jika setelah lulus,
kita memilih jalan yang berbeda,

240
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:22,090
hingga tak bisa bertemu lagi.

241
00:12:22,860 --> 00:12:26,180
Lalu, saat sudah dewasa nanti,
apa yang akan kita bicarakan, ya?

242
00:12:26,450 --> 00:12:28,730
Bodoh. Takkan ada yang berubah.

243
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:29,530
Eh?

244
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:31,920
Kita akan selalu berteman.

245
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,090
Ah!

246
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,980
Dia berada di sini, ya?

247
00:12:42,310 --> 00:12:43,070
Ya.

248
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:46,310
Ya, katanya dia dipercaya
mengelola kelab kabaret ini.

249
00:12:46,770 --> 00:12:49,460
Apa tak masalah kalau
kita tiba-tiba datang?

250
00:12:49,730 --> 00:12:52,280
Dia yang sekarang itu
petinggi Touman, loh.

251
00:12:52,530 --> 00:12:56,700
Mau dia petinggi Touman atau apalah,
Akkun tetaplah Akkun.

252
00:12:57,120 --> 00:13:02,510
Walau suaranya di telepon kayak orang dewasa,
tetapi dia masih sama seperti dulu.

253
00:13:02,910 --> 00:13:07,070
Aku cemas karena kau dengan jujur
bilang ingin bertemu Mikey.

254
00:13:07,290 --> 00:13:08,200
Kenapa?

255
00:13:08,450 --> 00:13:12,610
Kau terlalu blak-blakan.
Bahkan polisi pun sulit mendekati Mikey.

256
00:13:12,950 --> 00:13:15,130
Mungkin saja kita datang
untuk dibunuh.

257
00:13:15,310 --> 00:13:17,360
Kau bodoh banget, ya!

258
00:13:17,430 --> 00:13:20,620
Persahabatan takkan
berubah semudah itu!

259
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:23,110
Sudahlah, ikuti aku!

260
00:13:28,010 --> 00:13:30,130
Selamat datang!
Siapa nama Anda?

261
00:13:30,630 --> 00:13:32,460
Eh? Anu ....

262
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,960
Kau baik-baik saja?

263
00:13:34,150 --> 00:13:37,280
Kami ingin bertemu dengan Pak Sendou.

264
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:40,160
Kau ingin bertemu direktur kami?

265
00:13:40,170 --> 00:13:40,890
Iya!

266
00:13:41,060 --> 00:13:43,950
Oi! Ada gembel datang, nih.

267
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:45,640
Apa direktur punya janji temu?

268
00:13:47,180 --> 00:13:50,420
Aduh, bilang dari awal dong, Pak Hanagaki!

269
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:53,920
Kalau Anda sahabatnya Pak Direktur,
pasti akan langsung saya layani!

270
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:56,630
Saya akan mengantar
kalian ke ruang VIP!

271
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:58,630
Dia pasti mencemoohku, 'kan?

272
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:00,630
Kurasa tidak.

273
00:14:04,270 --> 00:14:07,440
Tanganmu gemetaran, Takemichi.

274
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:09,250
Aku enggak takut!

275
00:14:10,060 --> 00:14:11,130
Tenang saja!

276
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:15,910
Sekalipun status sosial kami berbeda,
dan dia telah menjadi orang hebat ....

277
00:14:16,380 --> 00:14:17,960
Akkun tetaplah Akkun!

278
00:14:18,250 --> 00:14:18,990
Eh?

279
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:20,520
Takemichi.

280
00:14:22,490 --> 00:14:23,980
Di belakangmu.

281
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:31,450
Kau tetaplah sama, Takemichi.

282
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:32,390
(Petinggi Geng Tokyo Manji - Sendou Atsushi)

283
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,080
Akkun!

284
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:37,940
Apa kau tak sadar karena
gaya rambutku berbeda?

285
00:14:38,010 --> 00:14:39,320
I-Iya.

286
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:42,780
Tadinya, aku ingin menyapamu lebih cepat.

287
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:45,300
Tapi aku terbawa
suasana nostalgia.

288
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:47,460
Meskipun Akkun ...

289
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:49,390
... penampilannya jauh berbeda,

290
00:14:49,700 --> 00:14:51,130
tetapi dia tetaplah Akkun!

291
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:54,320
Kau ingin bertemu dengan Bang Mikey, ya?

292
00:14:54,820 --> 00:15:00,110
Aku sudah lama menanti
kedatanganmu, Takemichi.

293
00:15:00,510 --> 00:15:02,040
Apa maksudmu?

294
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:05,950
Ayo bicara di luar.

295
00:15:08,740 --> 00:15:10,920
Berdua saja.
Boleh?

296
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:11,780
Ya.

297
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:15,160
- Aku tunggu di sini.
- Ya.

298
00:15:16,560 --> 00:15:17,430
Hati-hati.

299
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:19,420
Tenang saja.

300
00:15:20,010 --> 00:15:21,950
Jangan cemas!

301
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:32,340
Apa kau sehat, Takemichi?

302
00:15:32,420 --> 00:15:35,090
Adududuh!
Sakit, Akkun!

303
00:15:36,140 --> 00:15:40,510
Aku senang bisa bertemu lagi denganmu.
Sejak saat itu, waktu sudah cukup berlalu, ya!

304
00:15:41,880 --> 00:15:43,850
Di saat penting, Yamagishi malah ...

305
00:15:43,970 --> 00:15:45,820
... kentut dan mengacaukannya?!

306
00:15:45,890 --> 00:15:48,830
Iya. Padahal aku sudah bulatkan tekad!

307
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:52,590
Dulu, kau norak banget, ya.

308
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:55,050
Sejak SMP, ya.

309
00:15:55,370 --> 00:15:56,190
Ya.

310
00:15:56,930 --> 00:15:59,710
Dari sudut pandangmu,
kira-kira sudah 10 tahun, ya.

311
00:16:02,180 --> 00:16:04,500
Tapi, kau memang hebat, Akkun.

312
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:08,900
Kau memiliki kelab kabaret sebesar ini,
sekaligus petinggi Touman.

313
00:16:09,340 --> 00:16:10,330
Yah.

314
00:16:10,590 --> 00:16:14,720
Bisa menyetir mobil mewah, kenakan
pakaian mahal, dan gaet cewek bahenol!

315
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:17,440
Duniamu sangat berbeda dariku!

316
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:20,590
Itu karena kutahu caranya
mendapatkan uang.

317
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:23,800
Aku juga mau mengatakan kalimat itu!

318
00:16:24,720 --> 00:16:27,240
Orang yang bersamamu itu polisi, 'kan?

319
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:28,270
Eh?

320
00:16:28,650 --> 00:16:29,760
Eng ....

321
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:32,370
Tak usah disembunyikan,
soalnya terlihat jelas.

322
00:16:33,690 --> 00:16:35,480
Dia adiknya Tachibana, 'kan?

323
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:39,570
Aku tidak tahu kalau
dia memiliki adik.

324
00:16:40,580 --> 00:16:42,990
Kenapa kau tahu hal itu?

325
00:16:45,070 --> 00:16:48,700
Karena Geng Tokyo Manji
adalah organisasi yang seperti itu.

326
00:16:51,180 --> 00:16:54,380
Hei, ingatkah kau?
Saat musim panas di kelas 2 SMP.

327
00:16:54,550 --> 00:16:57,050
Saat kau menentang Kiyomasa.

328
00:16:57,560 --> 00:17:01,260
Setelah yang lain pulang,
kau berkata begini padaku.

329
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:06,430
Kalau kita tercerai-berai,
lalu bertemu lagi saat dewasa,

330
00:17:06,690 --> 00:17:09,140
kira-kira apa yang kita bicarakan?

331
00:17:09,950 --> 00:17:12,260
Ya! Aku ingat!

332
00:17:13,339 --> 00:17:15,410
Bagaimana kalau membicarakan ini?

333
00:17:16,599 --> 00:17:19,470
Yakni, pelaku yang
mendorongmu dari peron ...

334
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:21,700
... adalah aku.

335
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:28,620
Eh?

336
00:17:29,520 --> 00:17:31,720
Harusnya kau sudah terbunuh.

337
00:17:32,670 --> 00:17:34,670
Tapi, ada orang yang menolongmu.

338
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:37,380
Orang itu Tachibana Naoto!

339
00:17:37,990 --> 00:17:42,750
Saat itu, dia tampak tahu kalau
kau akan jatuh ke peron.

340
00:17:43,660 --> 00:17:45,430
Meski perkataanku aneh,

341
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:49,680
tapi apa kau kembali ke masa lalu?

342
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:54,440
Apa kau minta tolong pada
Tachibana Naoto di masa lalu?

343
00:17:54,740 --> 00:17:57,520
Benar, 'kan?
Kalau tidak, pasti aneh!

344
00:17:57,600 --> 00:18:00,910
Dia tak bisa menolongmu kalau
tidak tahu apa yang akan terjadi!

345
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:03,500
Hei!
Aneh, 'kan?

346
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:04,830
Hentikanlah!

347
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:08,770
Yang aneh itu siapa?
Kau bicara apa, Akkun?!

348
00:18:09,040 --> 00:18:10,910
Kau tidaklah seperti itu!

349
00:18:11,310 --> 00:18:13,740
Kau selalu kalem.

350
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:18,650
Kau mau berkorban demi temanmu.

351
00:18:19,330 --> 00:18:22,730
Kau sangat baik,
dan dapat diandalkan.

352
00:18:23,700 --> 00:18:24,970
Makanya ....

353
00:18:25,380 --> 00:18:26,700
Makanya ....

354
00:18:26,910 --> 00:18:28,600
Ucapanmu pasti bohong!

355
00:18:29,580 --> 00:18:32,330
Mana mungkin kau berniat membunuhku!

356
00:18:32,560 --> 00:18:35,380
Karena kau adalah temanku!

357
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:44,110
Takemichi.

358
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,080
Ya.

359
00:18:46,740 --> 00:18:49,610
Sejak kapan semuanya jadi begini, ya?

360
00:18:49,850 --> 00:18:50,750
Hah?

361
00:18:51,120 --> 00:18:54,190
Saat ini, aku prajuritnya Kisaki.

362
00:18:54,430 --> 00:18:57,190
Kisaki itu ... maksudnya Kisaki Tetta?!

363
00:18:57,320 --> 00:19:00,520
Semua anggota Touman
adalah bawahannya Kisaki.

364
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:03,650
Aku sudah tak bertemu
Bang Mikey bertahun-tahun.

365
00:19:05,340 --> 00:19:06,510
Akkun.

366
00:19:07,100 --> 00:19:10,960
Sekarang masih belum telat.
Keluarlah dari Touman!

367
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:13,690
Mustahil.

368
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:16,450
Aku takut.

369
00:19:17,180 --> 00:19:19,150
Takut pada Kisaki.

370
00:19:20,540 --> 00:19:21,630
Akkun.

371
00:19:26,810 --> 00:19:28,020
Takemichi.

372
00:19:29,930 --> 00:19:32,860
Mikey berubah sejak kematian Draken.

373
00:19:33,140 --> 00:19:33,830
Eh?

374
00:19:34,520 --> 00:19:36,010
Draken mati?!

375
00:19:37,040 --> 00:19:39,070
Dia tidak seharusnya mati.

376
00:19:39,760 --> 00:19:42,500
Draken yang tidak seharusnya mati,
tetapi malah mati.

377
00:19:43,010 --> 00:19:45,600
Lalu, aku mendapatkan uang
dengan cara kotor.

378
00:19:47,340 --> 00:19:49,770
Aku selalu mengaguminya.

379
00:19:49,900 --> 00:19:52,560
Mengagumi sosokmu yang
berjuang sambil menangis.

380
00:19:53,120 --> 00:19:54,150
Akkun!

381
00:19:55,620 --> 00:20:00,140
Yang ingin kau selamatkan dengan
kembali ke masa lalu ... adalah dia?

382
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,940
Di sana bahaya.

383
00:20:02,320 --> 00:20:03,520
Turunlah.

384
00:20:03,940 --> 00:20:05,980
Cinta sejati, ya.

385
00:20:07,950 --> 00:20:09,940
Berjuanglah, Takemichi.

386
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:10,720
Hah?

387
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:14,900
Selamatkanlah mereka.

388
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:16,640
Akkun!

389
00:20:17,270 --> 00:20:18,860
Wahai pahlawan cengeng.

390
00:20:18,970 --> 00:20:20,600
Jangan, Akkun!

391
00:20:20,820 --> 00:20:22,190
Akkun!

392
00:20:43,160 --> 00:20:43,860
Ah!

393
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:22,420
Mohon maaf,
biarkanlah dia untuk sementara.

394
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,260
Tak apa.

395
00:21:24,810 --> 00:21:26,580
Mereka ingin bertanya, 'kan?

396
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:34,180
Jangan paksakan dirimu.

397
00:21:34,850 --> 00:21:36,570
Istirahatlah sejenak.

398
00:21:37,280 --> 00:21:38,440
Naoto.

399
00:21:40,130 --> 00:21:42,780
Selidikilah hari kematian Ryuguji Ken.

400
00:21:43,020 --> 00:21:44,040
Eh?

401
00:21:45,420 --> 00:21:48,860
Kisaki Tetta-lah yang menjadikan
Touman sebagai geng jahat.

402
00:21:50,170 --> 00:21:51,370
Naoto.

403
00:21:51,770 --> 00:21:53,390
Aku ....

404
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:57,390
Baik Draken, Akkun,

405
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:00,700
maupun Hina,

406
00:22:04,450 --> 00:22:07,690
aku ingin menyelamatkan mereka!

407
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:26,880
Dengan berjalan di sisimu yang
agak bau keringat

408
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:29,790
itu sudah cukup bagiku

409
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:35,810
Seraya dihantam oleh hujan tiba-tiba,

410
00:22:35,820 --> 00:22:39,320
kita berciuman di tengah dinginnya malam

411
00:22:41,220 --> 00:22:49,070
Kala aku berpaling, masihlah ada
diriku yang kerap tertawa

412
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:50,250
Tolonglah!

413
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:57,220
Hei, ayo menuju masa depan yang
tak mungkin terwujud!

414
00:22:57,260 --> 00:22:59,710
Bawalah aku sekarang juga

415
00:22:59,730 --> 00:23:01,720
ke dunia baru

416
00:23:01,730 --> 00:23:06,440
olehmu yang kusebut sebagai "pahlawanku"

417
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:08,450
Harapan yang blak-blakan

418
00:23:08,470 --> 00:23:10,760
melampaui waktu yang terhenti

419
00:23:10,820 --> 00:23:15,710
"Tiada lagi yang kubutuhkan selainmu"

420
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:23,590
Aku akan selalu bernapas di sini

421
00:23:29,930 --> 00:23:32,100
Hancurkan jarum yang bengkok

422
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:34,400
dengan suara tegas

423
00:23:34,410 --> 00:23:36,810
lalu empaskan takdir!


